{"tid":2191812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃店店長車被皇軍拖走","createTime":"2020-09-06T16:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T23:19:05.000Z","uid":23707,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"15852832b24f02feea73dab2e0dd63a53485ed4c","tid":2191812,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1255031384840268/?vh=e&amp;extid=HBpSi5wokYgeUz34&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1255031384840268%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3DHBpSi5wokYgeUz34%26d%3Dn&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4q7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=8ff6567e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1255031384840268/?vh=e&amp;extid=HBpSi5wokYgeUz34&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［黃店店主車被警拖走扣查］警方於晚上九時半突然到旺角甘霖街截查一輛私家車，據警方表示，該車輛因不適宜在道路行駛，對其他道路使用者帶來危險，並將之拖走扣查。<br />\n<br />\n該車車主為附近一間食店東主陳先生所有，他指事發時突然一輛防暴車駛至，有街坊通知他要將車駛走，陳先生準備開車時，即遭警員截查，隨後有交通警到場，指其車為「光頭軚」。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生稱，他於今年年頭才換車軚，行駛不足2萬公里，故要等到警方檢驗結果才能確定是否有問題。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生所經營之食店在網上被稱為「黃店」，主要賣燒烤食品及車仔麵，至於是否因此而受查，他表示不能排除此原因。"},{"pid":"97db37a1bb39082ff370fd2fe36c3ce20d3d0da8","tid":2191812,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46699ef193e10b3ef0638d68dd73e4611af923ba","tid":2191812,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ad67a01b7114c26ab16400955864f099f7fb1868","tid":2191812,"uid":67655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"皇軍想點就點"},{"pid":"7da5756aea887b270df87d05ef0f4fb89905a655","tid":2191812,"uid":305292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco